STATE
v.
Randall GREENOUGH. No. 151P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 6, 2005. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, James E. Hardin, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 16th day of March 2005 by Defendant for Appropriate Relief:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of April 2005."
